{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"HTML 导入（HTML Imports）","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/conflicting/Web/Web_Components","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Guides</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/Web_Components/Using_custom_elements\">Using custom elements</a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/Web_Components/Using_shadow_DOM\">Using shadow DOM</a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/Web_Components/Using_templates_and_slots\">Using templates and slots</a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Interfaces</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CustomElementRegistry\"><code>CustomElementRegistry</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/HTMLSlotElement\"><code>HTMLSlotElement</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/HTMLTemplateElement\"><code>HTMLTemplateElement</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/ShadowRoot\"><code>ShadowRoot</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>属性</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Element/shadowRoot\"><code>Element.shadowRoot</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Element/slot\"><code>Element.slot</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Event/composed\"><code>Event.composed</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Event/composedPath\"><code>Event.composedPath</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Node/isConnected\"><code>Node.isConnected</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Window/customElements\"><code>Window.customElements</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>方法</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Document/createElement\"><code>Document.createElement()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Element/attachShadow\"><code>Element.attachShadow()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Node/getRootNode\"><code>Node.getRootNode()</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>\n\n<div class=\"obsolete notecard\" id=\"sect1\">\n<p><strong>在 Google&nbsp;Chrome&nbsp;73 后已过时</strong><br>\n 此功能已过时。虽然它可能仍然适用于某些浏览器，但不鼓励使用它，因为它随时可能被删除。尽量避免使用它。</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"warning notecard\" id=\"sect2\">\n<p>Firefox 将不会以当前形式发布HTML导入特性，<font><font>有关</font><font>&nbsp;更多信息，</font><font>请参阅此</font></font><a href=\"https://hacks.mozilla.org/2015/06/the-state-of-web-components/\" rel=\"noopener\" class=\"external\"><font><font>状态更新</font></font></a>。<font><font>在对标准达成共识或制定替代机制之前，您可以使用Google等的polyfill&nbsp;</font></font><code><a href=\"https://github.com/webcomponents/webcomponentsjs\" rel=\"noopener\" class=\"external\">webcomponents.js</a></code><font><font>。</font></font>&nbsp;</p>\n</div>\n\n<p><strong>HTML Imports&nbsp;</strong>旨在成为 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/Web_Components\">Web Components</a> 的打包机制，但也可以单独使用 HTML Imports。</p>\n\n<div id=\"sect3\">可以在HTML文档中使用<code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/link\">&lt;link&gt;</a></code> 标记导入HTML文件，如下所示：</div>\n\n<div id=\"sect4\">&nbsp;</div>\n\n<pre class=\"notranslate\">&lt;link rel=\"import\" href=\"myfile.html\"&gt;</pre>\n\n<p><span style=\"line-height: 1.5;\">链接类型&nbsp;</span><code style=\"font-style: normal; line-height: 1.5;\">import</code><span style=\"line-height: 1.5;\">&nbsp;是新加入的。</span></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"规范","title":"规范","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"spec-table standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">规范</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">状态</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">评论</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://w3c.github.io/webcomponents/spec/imports/\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" title=\"HTML Imports\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML Imports</a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-wd\">Working Draft</span></td>\n   <td>初步定义</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性","isH3":false,"data":null,"query":"html.elements.link.rel.import","browsers":null}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"阅读更多","title":"<strong>阅读更多:</strong>","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li>https://developer.mozilla.org/zh-CN/docs/Web/Web_Components</li>\n <li>https://developer.mozilla.org/zh-CN/docs/Web/Web_Components/Custom_Elements</li>\n <li>https://developer.mozilla.org/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/template</li>\n <li>https://developer.mozilla.org/zh-CN/docs/Web/Web_Components/Shadow_DOM<br>\n  &nbsp;</li>\n</ul>","titleAsText":"阅读更多:"}}],"toc":[{"text":"规范","id":"规范"},{"text":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性"},{"text":"<strong>阅读更多:</strong>","id":"阅读更多"}],"summary":"HTML Imports 旨在成为 Web Components 的打包机制，但也可以单独使用 HTML Imports。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"HTML インポート","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"HTML Импорты","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/conflicting/web/web_components","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/conflicting/web/web_components/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"pageTitle":"HTML 导入（HTML Imports） | MDN","noIndexing":true}}